		<div id="comment_body_64552127">Criminals are now emboldened as a result of them paying the ransom? File that under "Duh". The only solution is to make paying the ransom a federal crime. The current approach of appeasement isn't working. Make the money source dry up for the criminals and give organizations only one possible means of protection: improve their security.</div>
	</div>

	<div class="commentSub" id="comment_sub_64552127">
